These Grafana dashboards provide a centralized view of key engineering and delivery metrics across projects, including test automation maturity, GitHub Copilot adoption, consultant performance, and upcoming Agile and DevOpsSec insights. By consolidating data from multiple sources into structured reports, they improve transparency, support data-driven decision-making, and help teams track progress, productivity, and overall delivery effectiveness. The dashboards enable better visibility into testing activities, tool usage, and performance trends across the organization.
